 IT12.1     Retain a portion of agency information technology savings for 
 reinvestment. 
<p>
 IT12.2     Promote performance-based contracting for information 
 technology. 
<p>
 IT13.1     Establish a program to train nontechnical senior executives 
 and political appointees in information technology. 
 
