 D.C.: U.S. General Accounting Office, November 1991), p. 1.
<p>
 3. Personal Interview with Dick Whitford, Acting Assistant Director, 
 Affirmative Recruitment and Employment, Office of Personnel 
 Management, Washington, D.C., August 1993.
<p>
