<p>
 3. U.S. General Accounting Office, Quality Management: Survey of 
 Federal Organizations, GAO/GGD-93-9BR (Washington, D.C.: GAO, October 
 1992), p. 2. 
<p>
 4. National Academy of Public Administration (NAPA), Leading People 
 in Change: Empowerment, Commitment, Accountability (Washington, D.C., 
