<p>
 5. GAO, Federal Labor Relations, p. 2.
<p>
 6. Goodwin, Larry K. "Win-Win Negotiations: A Model for Cooperative 
 Labor Relations," The Public Manager (Potomac, MD, Summer 1993), p. 
 19.
<p>
 7. GAO, Federal Labor Relations, p. 76.
<p>
