<DOCNO>WT27-B14-40</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000294-B035-105</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.npr.gov:80/library/reports/pd04.html 192.239.92.66 19970120075351 text/html 6126
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 07:54:09 GMT
