<P>
Appendices
<HR>
<P>
<H2> Appendix A:  Summary of Actions by Implementation Category</H2>
 <p>
 (2) President, Executive Office of the President, or 
     Office of Management and Budget can do
<p> 
 DES01: Activate Program Design as a Formal 
Discipline
<p> 
 DES02: Establish Pilot Program Design Capabilities 
in One or Two Agencies
