<H2>Transforming Organizational Structure</H2>
<p>
Appendices
<HR>
<p>
<H2> Appendix B: Illustrative Table of Areas of Management Control that Should be 
 Considered as Potential Targets for Streamlining</h2>
 <p>
<p> 
<b> Numbers of Personnel</b>
 <p>
  <pre>
