<p>
<p>3. Ibid.
<p>
<p>4. General Education Provisions Act (GEPA), Section 431(d)(1).
<p>
<p>5. Immigration and Naturalization Service v. Chadha, 103 S.Ct. 2764 
 (1983).
<p>
<p>6. GEPA, Section 431(g).
<p>
<p>7. Ibid., Section 431(a)(2).
<p>
