<p>
<p>4. U.S. Office of Personnel Management, Training in the Federal 
 Service, Fiscal Year 1988 (Washington, D.C., 1987), pp. 20-21.
<p>
<p>5. GAO, Department of Education: Long-Standing Management Problems 
 Hamper Reforms, p. 40.
<p>
<p>6. Interview with Dr. Terry Newell, Director, Horace Mann Learning 
