<DOCHDR>
http://www.npr.gov:80/library/reports/EPA3.html 192.239.92.66 19970120085502 text/html 26498
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 08:55:13 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
