<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000295-B039-200</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.npr.gov:80/library/reports/EPA9.html 192.239.92.66 19970120085924 text/html 10680
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 08:59:38 GMT
