<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000295-B041-137</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.npr.gov:80/library/reports/FEMA2.html 192.239.92.66 19970120090512 text/html 11305
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 09:05:19 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
